  <rdfs:label xml:lang="en">[2023-02-23/2021-01-28]: Stockbridge-Munsee Tribal Council Res. No. 1551-95</rdfs:label>
    <oll:dateAdopted rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date">1995-11-07</oll:dateAdopted>
    <oll:dateEffective rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date">1996-07-18</oll:dateEffective>
    <oll:history>Adopted the Mohican Judiciary Act containing revised Court Code, revised General Citation Ordinance, and the Stockbridge-Munsee Bill of Rights. Mohican Judiciary Act forwarded to BIA for their review and approval on December 15, 1995. Comments from BIA on July 5, 1996.</oll:history>
